@page "/agents/supplier-coordinator"

<PageTitle>Supplier Coordinator Agent — Claims Team in a Day</PageTitle>

<div class="agent-header" style="--accent: #10b981">
    <a class="back-link" href="/"><span aria-hidden="true">←</span> Back to claims office</a>
    <div class="agent-header-row">
        <div class="agent-header-icon">🛠️</div>
        <div>
            <div class="agent-header-dept">Supplier Coordination</div>
            <h1>Supplier Coordinator Agent</h1>
            <div class="agent-header-persona">Sam — Supplier Coordinator</div>
            <p class="tagline">Books the right repairer at the right time and chases overdue jobs.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="agent-tab-scope" style="--accent: #10b981">
    <nav class="agent-tabs" role="tablist" aria-label="Supplier Coordinator agent details">
        <button type="button" class="agent-tab active" data-tab="overview" role="tab" aria-selected="true" tabindex="0">Overview</button>
        <button type="button" class="agent-tab" data-tab="try" role="tab" aria-selected="false" tabindex="-1">Try it out</button>
    </nav>

    <div class="agent-tab-panel active" data-panel="overview" role="tabpanel">
    <section class="panel" style="--accent: #10b981">
        <h2>What this agent does</h2>
        <p>
            Recommends approved suppliers, schedules inspections and repairs, tracks SLAs,
            and keeps the claim file updated with supplier status.
        </p>
        <div class="two-col">
            <div>
                <h3>Responsibilities</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Match the loss to a suitable supplier in the customer's area.</li>
                    <li>Request quotes and book inspection or repair appointments.</li>
                    <li>Track SLA breaches and chase overdue suppliers.</li>
                    <li>Compare quotes against the approved scope of loss.</li>
                    <li>Draft customer-facing booking confirmations.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h3>Tools available</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Supplier directory (MCP <code>lookupSuppliers</code>) — best-price match across approved network</li>
                    <li>Quote request PDF generator (MCP <code>generateQuoteRequestPdf</code>)</li>
                    <li>Appointment scheduler</li>
                    <li>SLA tracker</li>
                    <li>Invoice matcher</li>
                </ul>
                <h3>Human approval</h3>
                <p class="approval">
                    Required for non-preferred supplier, high-cost quotes, supplier disputes,
                    scope variations, or customer complaints about a supplier.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="panel" style="--accent: #10b981">
        <h2>How this agent helps with the claim</h2>
        <div class="demo">
            <p>
                Once a claim is approved, Sam's supplier coordinator agent matches the loss to
                the right supplier on Zava's approved network — by location, capacity, and SLA
                track record. It requests quotes, books appointments, and arranges any rental
                or temporary accommodation the policy supports.
            </p>
            <p>
                From there the agent quietly tracks every job: chasing overdue quotes, comparing
                invoices against the agreed scope, and drafting clear booking confirmations for
                the customer. Anything outside policy — a non-preferred supplier, an over-budget
                quote, a scope variation — is held for a human to approve before it goes ahead.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    </div>

    <div class="agent-tab-panel" data-panel="try" role="tabpanel">
    <section class="panel supplier-panel" style="--accent: #10b981">
        <h2>Try It Out — Supplier Coordination Demo</h2>
        <p class="muted supplier-help">
            Walk through how Sam's supplier coordinator agent picks up an approved
            claim, matches it to a suitable repairer / builder / assessor / hire
            car / temporary accommodation, dispatches a work order and drafts an
            update for the customer. Steps run live against the
            <code>/supplier/*</code> endpoints in this app.
        </p>

        <!-- Step 1 — pick a claim -->
        <div class="supplier-step" data-step="1">
            <div class="supplier-step-head">
                <span class="supplier-step-num">1</span>
                <h3>Pick a Claim ID</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="muted">
                Claim IDs come from the <a href="/agents/claims-intake">Claims Intake</a>
                demo and are held in memory for the rest of the demo flow. Lodge a
                claim there first if the dropdown is empty.
            </p>
            <div class="supplier-pick">
                <label for="supplier-claim-select">Claim</label>
                <select id="supplier-claim-select"></select>
                <button type="button" id="supplier-refresh-btn" class="supplier-refresh" title="Reload claim list">↻</button>
            </div>
            <div class="supplier-claim-summary" id="supplier-claim-summary" hidden></div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 2 — engage the agent -->
        <div class="supplier-step" data-step="2">
            <div class="supplier-step-head">
                <span class="supplier-step-num">2</span>
                <h3>Engage Supplier Coordinator Agent</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="muted">
                The agent reviews the claim, matches it to a supplier on Zava's
                approved network, proposes appointment slots, dispatches a work
                order and drafts a plain-English update for the customer.
            </p>
            <button id="supplier-process-btn" type="button" disabled>Engage Supplier Coordinator Agent</button>
            <div id="supplier-process-status" class="supplier-status" hidden></div>
            <div id="supplier-agent-notes" class="supplier-notes" hidden>
                <div class="supplier-notes-label">Agent narrative</div>
                <div id="supplier-agent-notes-body" class="agent-md"></div>
            </div>

            <div class="engage-tabs-scope" data-engage-role="supplier">
                <div class="engage-tabs" role="tablist">
                    <button type="button" class="engage-tab-btn active" data-engage-tab="prompt">Agent Prompt &amp; Tools</button>
                    <button type="button" class="engage-tab-btn" data-engage-tab="input">Agent Input</button>
                    <button type="button" class="engage-tab-btn" data-engage-tab="output">Raw Output</button>
                </div>

                <div class="engage-tab-panel active" data-engage-tab="prompt">
                    <div class="engage-info-block">
                        <h4>Agent metadata</h4>
                        <div class="engage-info-meta engage-meta"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="engage-info-block">
                        <h4>System prompt</h4>
                        <pre class="engage-pre engage-prompt-body">Loading…</pre>
                    </div>
                    <div class="engage-info-block">
                        <h4>Tools available</h4>
                        <ul class="engage-tools-list"><li class="engage-empty">Loading…</li></ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="engage-tab-panel" data-engage-tab="input">
                    <div class="engage-info-block">
                        <h4>Prompt sent to the agent</h4>
                        <pre class="engage-pre engage-input-body engage-empty">Engage the agent to capture the input that was sent.</pre>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="engage-tab-panel" data-engage-tab="output">
                    <div class="engage-info-block">
                        <h4>Raw agent output (text, citations, every output item including tool / function calls)</h4>
                        <div class="json-viewer engage-output-body"><div class="engage-empty">Engage the agent to see the full raw response.</div></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 3 — match results -->
        <div class="supplier-step" data-step="3" id="supplier-result" hidden>
            <div class="supplier-step-head">
                <span class="supplier-step-num">3</span>
                <h3>Recommended supplier &amp; appointment options</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="supplier-result-grid">
                <div class="supplier-card">
                    <div class="supplier-card-label">Recommended</div>
                    <div class="supplier-card-name" id="supplier-rec-name"></div>
                    <div class="supplier-card-meta" id="supplier-rec-specialty"></div>
                    <div class="supplier-card-meta" id="supplier-rec-location"></div>
                    <div class="supplier-card-meta">
                        <span class="supplier-pill" id="supplier-rec-rating"></span>
                        <span class="supplier-pill" id="supplier-rec-sla"></span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <div class="supplier-card-label">Appointment options</div>
                    <ul class="supplier-appts" id="supplier-appts"></ul>
                    <div class="supplier-card-label" style="margin-top: 0.6rem;">Alternatives</div>
                    <ul class="supplier-alts" id="supplier-alts"></ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 4 — work order + customer update -->
        <div class="supplier-step" data-step="4" id="supplier-dispatch" hidden>
            <div class="supplier-step-head">
                <span class="supplier-step-num">4</span>
                <h3>Work order dispatched</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="supplier-wo">
                <div class="supplier-wo-head">
                    <span class="supplier-wo-num" id="supplier-wo-num"></span>
                    <span class="supplier-wo-status">Dispatched</span>
                </div>
                <div class="supplier-wo-row"><span class="k">Scope</span><span id="supplier-wo-scope"></span></div>
                <div class="supplier-wo-row"><span class="k">ETA</span><span id="supplier-wo-eta"></span></div>
                <div class="supplier-wo-row"><span class="k">Type</span><span id="supplier-wo-type"></span></div>
            </div>

            <div class="supplier-customer">
                <div class="supplier-customer-label">Customer update — draft</div>
                <div id="supplier-customer-body" class="agent-md"></div>
            </div>

            <div class="supplier-pdf" id="supplier-pdf" hidden>
                <div class="supplier-pdf-label">Quote request PDF</div>
                <div class="supplier-pdf-row">
                    <span class="supplier-pdf-icon" aria-hidden="true">📄</span>
                    <div class="supplier-pdf-meta">
                        <div class="supplier-pdf-name" id="supplier-pdf-name"></div>
                        <div class="supplier-pdf-sub" id="supplier-pdf-sub"></div>
                    </div>
                    <a id="supplier-pdf-link" class="supplier-pdf-btn" href="#" download>Download PDF</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="supplier-approval" id="supplier-approval" hidden>
                <span class="supplier-approval-pill">Human approval required</span>
                <span id="supplier-approval-reason"></span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    .supplier-panel { --supplier-accent: #10b981; }
    .supplier-help { margin-bottom: 0.9rem; }
    .supplier-help code { background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.12); padding: 1px 6px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.85rem; }

    .supplier-step {
        border: 1px solid rgba(120, 150, 200, 0.18);
        background: rgba(15, 22, 38, 0.4);
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 0.95rem 1.1rem 1rem 1.1rem;
        margin-top: 0.9rem;
    }
    .supplier-step-head { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.6rem; margin-bottom: 0.3rem; }
    .supplier-step-head h3 { margin: 0; color: #fff; font-size: 1rem; }
    .supplier-step-num {
        display: inline-grid; place-items: center;
        width: 1.55rem; height: 1.55rem;
        border-radius: 50%;
        background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--supplier-accent) 22%, rgba(20, 28, 46, 0.7));
        border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--supplier-accent) 55%, transparent);
        color: var(--supplier-accent);
        font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 700;
    }
    .supplier-step .muted { color: var(--zava-muted, #97a3b6); font-size: 0.9rem; margin: 0.35rem 0 0.7rem 0; }
    .supplier-step .muted a { color: var(--supplier-accent); }

    .supplier-pick {
        display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.6rem;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .supplier-pick label {
        font-size: 0.7rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        color: var(--zava-muted, #97a3b6); font-weight: 700;
    }
    .supplier-pick select {
        background: rgba(10, 16, 28, 0.7);
        border: 1px solid rgba(120, 150, 200, 0.22);
        border-radius: 6px;
        color: #fff;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        padding: 0.5rem 0.7rem;
        min-width: 280px;
    }
    .supplier-pick select:focus {
        outline: none;
        border-color: var(--supplier-accent);
        box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px color-mix(in srgb, var(--supplier-accent) 25%, transparent);
    }
    .supplier-refresh {
        background: transparent;
        color: rgba(238, 242, 247, 0.86);
        border: 1px solid rgba(120, 150, 200, 0.32);
        border-radius: 6px;
        padding: 0.4rem 0.7rem;
        font-size: 1rem;
        cursor: pointer;
    }
    .supplier-refresh:hover { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05); color: #fff; }

    .supplier-claim-summary {
        margin-top: 0.7rem;
        background: rgba(10, 16, 28, 0.7);
        border: 1px solid rgba(120, 150, 200, 0.18);
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 0.7rem 0.85rem;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr));
        gap: 0.5rem 1rem;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        color: rgba(238, 242, 247, 0.86);
    }
    .supplier-claim-summary .k {
        display: block;
        font-size: 0.66rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        color: var(--zava-muted, #97a3b6); font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.15rem;
    }

    #supplier-process-btn {
        background: var(--supplier-accent);
        color: #04241a;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
        font-size: 0.88rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        cursor: pointer;
        margin-top: 0.35rem;
    }
    #supplier-process-btn:disabled { opacity: 0.5; cursor: not-allowed; }

    .supplier-status {
        margin-top: 0.6rem; font-size: 0.88rem;
        color: rgba(238, 242, 247, 0.88);
    }
    .supplier-status.error { color: #fca5a5; }
    .supplier-status .spinner {
        display: inline-block; width: 12px; height: 12px;
        border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3); border-top-color: #fff;
        border-radius: 50%; margin-right: 6px; vertical-align: middle;
        animation: supplier-spin 0.7s linear infinite;
    }
    @@keyframes supplier-spin { to { transform: rotate(360deg); } }

    .supplier-notes {
        margin-top: 0.7rem;
        background: rgba(10, 16, 28, 0.7);
        border: 1px solid rgba(120, 150, 200, 0.18);
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 0.7rem 0.85rem;
    }
    .supplier-notes-label {
        font-size: 0.66rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.12em;
        color: var(--zava-muted, #97a3b6); font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
    }
    .supplier-notes pre {
        color: rgba(238, 242, 247, 0.86);
        font-size: 0.82rem;
        line-height: 1.5;
        white-space: pre-wrap;
        margin: 0;
        font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, monospace;
    }

    .supplier-result-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 0.85rem;
    }
    @@media (max-width: 820px) { .supplier-result-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

    .supplier-card {
        background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--supplier-accent) 10%, rgba(15, 22, 38, 0.7));
        border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--supplier-accent) 35%, transparent);
        border-radius: 10px;
        padding: 0.8rem 0.95rem;
    }
    .supplier-card-label {
        font-size: 0.66rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.12em;
        color: var(--zava-muted, #97a3b6); font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
    }
    .supplier-card-name { color: #fff; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1rem; margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
    .supplier-card-meta { color: rgba(238, 242, 247, 0.86); font-size: 0.85rem; margin-top: 0.15rem; }
    .supplier-pill {
        display: inline-block;
        background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.12);
        border: 1px solid rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.4);
        color: #6ee7b7;
        padding: 0.1rem 0.55rem;
        border-radius: 999px;
        font-size: 0.72rem;
        margin-right: 0.35rem;
        margin-top: 0.3rem;
    }

    .supplier-appts, .supplier-alts {
        margin: 0.3rem 0 0 0;
        padding: 0;
        list-style: none;
    }
    .supplier-appts li {
        background: rgba(10, 16, 28, 0.7);
        border: 1px solid rgba(120, 150, 200, 0.18);
        border-radius: 6px;
        padding: 0.4rem 0.7rem;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        color: rgba(238, 242, 247, 0.9);
        margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
    }
    .supplier-alts li {
        font-size: 0.82rem;
        color: rgba(238, 242, 247, 0.78);
        padding: 0.2rem 0;
    }
    .supplier-alts li strong { color: #fff; font-weight: 600; }

    .supplier-wo {
        background: rgba(10, 16, 28, 0.7);
        border: 1px solid rgba(120, 150, 200, 0.18);
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 0.7rem 0.85rem;
    }
    .supplier-wo-head { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.6rem; margin-bottom: 0.45rem; }
    .supplier-wo-num {
        font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, monospace;
        color: #6ee7b7;
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 1rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }
    .supplier-wo-status {
        margin-left: auto;
        background: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.16);
        color: #86efac;
        border: 1px solid rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.4);
        padding: 0.1rem 0.55rem;
        border-radius: 999px;
        font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 700;
        text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    }
    .supplier-wo-row { font-size: 0.86rem; padding: 0.18rem 0; color: rgba(238, 242, 247, 0.86); }
    .supplier-wo-row .k {
        display: inline-block; min-width: 64px;
        color: var(--zava-muted, #97a3b6); font-weight: 600;
        text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 0.66rem; letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        margin-right: 0.5rem;
    }

    .supplier-customer {
        margin-top: 0.7rem;
        background: rgba(10, 16, 28, 0.7);
        border: 1px solid rgba(120, 150, 200, 0.18);
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 0.7rem 0.85rem;
    }
    .supplier-customer-label {
        font-size: 0.66rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.12em;
        color: var(--zava-muted, #97a3b6); font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
    }
    .supplier-customer pre {
        color: rgba(238, 242, 247, 0.9);
        font-size: 0.88rem;
        line-height: 1.5;
        white-space: pre-wrap;
        margin: 0;
        font-family: inherit;
    }

    .supplier-pdf {
        margin-top: 0.7rem;
        background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.08);
        border: 1px solid rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.35);
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 0.7rem 0.85rem;
    }
    .supplier-pdf-label {
        font-size: 0.66rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.12em;
        color: var(--zava-muted, #97a3b6); font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.45rem;
    }
    .supplier-pdf-row {
        display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.7rem;
    }
    .supplier-pdf-icon { font-size: 1.6rem; }
    .supplier-pdf-meta { flex: 1; min-width: 0; }
    .supplier-pdf-name {
        color: #fff; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.92rem;
        overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; white-space: nowrap;
    }
    .supplier-pdf-sub {
        color: var(--zava-muted, #97a3b6); font-size: 0.78rem; margin-top: 0.1rem;
    }
    .supplier-pdf-btn {
        background: var(--supplier-accent);
        color: #04241a;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 6px;
        padding: 0.4rem 0.85rem;
        font-size: 0.82rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        cursor: pointer;
        text-decoration: none;
        white-space: nowrap;
    }
    .supplier-pdf-btn:hover { filter: brightness(1.1); }

    .supplier-approval {
        margin-top: 0.7rem;
        background: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.10);
        border: 1px solid rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.4);
        color: #fcd34d;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 0.55rem 0.8rem;
        font-size: 0.86rem;
    }
    .supplier-approval-pill {
        display: inline-block;
        background: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.18);
        color: #fcd34d;
        border: 1px solid rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.4);
        padding: 0.1rem 0.55rem;
        border-radius: 999px;
        font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 700;
        text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em;
        margin-right: 0.5rem;
    }
</style>

